{
  "texts": [
    "55 presented a classification technique for urinary stones utilizing KUB x-ray images.",
    "They employed the least absolute shrinkage and selection operator (LASSO) algorithm with ML classifiers.",
    "This methodology yielded a classification accuracy of 96% for kidney stones.",
    "Jungmann et al.",
    "56 created an NLP technique trained on subjective assessment to automatically collect positive hit rates and clinical information to evaluate 1714 narrative LDCT reports."
  ]
}